   "source": [
    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Building a RAG Chatbot Using LlamaIndex\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"LlamaIndex provides users with a simple way of creating a chatbot that works both with an LLM and data from a database. This combination is called Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and is used to give LLM's the ability to answer queries using data it was not trained on. This notebook will cover each step necessary to create a RAG chatbot using the Python SDK for Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL. It demonstrates **7 search types** now available in `AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearch`:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| Search Type | Description |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"|---|---|\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `vector` | Standard nearest-neighbour via `VectorDistance`, ordered by score |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `vector_score_threshold` | Vector search filtered by a minimum similarity score |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `full_text_search` | `FullTextContains` WHERE predicate — no `query_embedding` needed |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `full_text_ranking` | `ORDER BY RANK FullTextScore(...)`, single or multi-field RRF — no `query_embedding` needed |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `hybrid` | `ORDER BY RANK RRF(FullTextScore, VectorDistance)` |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `hybrid_score_threshold` | Hybrid RRF + client-side score threshold filter |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"| `weighted_hybrid_search` | Hybrid RRF + client-side per-component weight re-ranking |\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"**Important Note:** This sample requires you to have Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL and Azure OpenAI accounts set up. To get started, visit:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- [Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL Python Quickstart](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/nosql/quickstart-python?pivots=devcontainer-codespace)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- [Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL Vector Search](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/nosql/vector-search)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"- [Azure OpenAI](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/ai-services/openai/)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 1. Install Dependencies\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789012\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"%pip install llama-index\\n\",\n",
    "    \"%pip install llama-index-embeddings-azure-openai\\n\",\n",
    "    \"%pip install llama-index-llms-azure-openai\\n\",\n",
    "    \"%pip install llama-index-vector-stores-azurecosmosnosql\\n\",\n",
    "    \"%pip install gradio\\n\",\n",
    "    \"%pip install python-dotenv\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d4e5f6a7-b8c9-0123-defa-234567890123\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 2. Setup Azure OpenAI\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Prior to beginning we need to set up the LLM and embedding model that will be used in the RAG chatbot.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e5f6a7b8-c9d0-1234-efab-345678901234\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import os\\n\",\n",
    "    \"import time\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from dotenv import load_dotenv\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.llms.azure_openai import AzureOpenAI\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.embeddings.azure_openai import AzureOpenAIEmbedding\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"load_dotenv()\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f6a7b8c9-d0e1-2345-fabc-456789012345\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT = os.getenv(\\\"AZURE_OPENAI_API_ENDPOINT\\\", \\\"YOUR_AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY  = os.getenv(\\\"AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY\\\",      \\\"YOUR_AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"COSMOS_DB_URI         = os.getenv(\\\"COSMOS_DB_URI\\\",              \\\"YOUR_AZURE_COSMOSDB_URI\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"COSMOS_DB_API_KEY     = os.getenv(\\\"COSMOS_DB_API_KEY\\\",          \\\"YOUR_AZURE_COSMOSDB_KEY\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"llm = AzureOpenAI(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    model=\\\"gpt-35-turbo\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    deployment_name=\\\"gpt-35-turbo\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    azure_endpoint=AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    api_key=AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    api_version=\\\"2023-05-15\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"embed_model = AzureOpenAIEmbedding(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    model=\\\"text-embedding-3-large\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    deployment_name=\\\"text-embedding-3-large\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    azure_endpoint=AZURE_OPENAI_ENDPOINT,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    api_key=AZURE_OPENAI_API_KEY,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    api_version=\\\"2023-05-15\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a7b8c9d0-e1f2-3456-abcd-567890123456\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 3. Load Data\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Load the data using the LlamaIndex `SimpleDirectoryReader`.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b8c9d0e1-f2a3-4567-bcde-678901234567\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import nest_asyncio\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.core import SimpleDirectoryReader, Document\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"nest_asyncio.apply()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"documents = SimpleDirectoryReader(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    input_dir=r\\\"../../DataSet/CVPR2019/abstracts_pdf\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \").load_data()\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c9d0e1f2-a3b4-5678-cdef-789012345678\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 4. Configure Global LlamaIndex Settings\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d0e1f2a3-b4c5-6789-defa-890123456789\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.core import Settings\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Settings.llm = llm\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Settings.embed_model = embed_model\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e1f2a3b4-c5d6-7890-efab-901234567890\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 5. Create the Vector Store and Index\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Initialize the Cosmos DB NoSQL client, configure the vector embedding and indexing policies, create the vector store, and index the documents.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f2a3b4c5-d6e7-8901-fabc-012345678901\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"from azure.cosmos import CosmosClient, PartitionKey\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.vector_stores.azurecosmosnosql import (\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearch,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.core import StorageContext, VectorStoreIndex\\n\",\n",
    "    \"from llama_index.core.vector_stores import VectorStoreQuery\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Create Cosmos DB client\\n\",\n",
    "    \"client = CosmosClient(COSMOS_DB_URI, credential=COSMOS_DB_API_KEY)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Vector indexing policy\\n\",\n",
    "    \"indexing_policy = {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"indexingMode\\\": \\\"consistent\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"includedPaths\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/*\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"excludedPaths\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": '/\\\"_etag\\\"/?'}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"vectorIndexes\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/embedding\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"quantizedFlat\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"vector_embedding_policy = {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"vectorEmbeddings\\\": [\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"path\\\": \\\"/embedding\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"dataType\\\": \\\"float32\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"distanceFunction\\\": \\\"cosine\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"            \\\"dimensions\\\": 3072,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        }\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ]\\n\",\n",
    "    \"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"partition_key = PartitionKey(path=\\\"/id\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"cosmos_container_properties = {\\\"partition_key\\\": partition_key}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"cosmos_database_properties = {}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Create vector store\\n\",\n",
    "    \"store = AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearch(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_client=client,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_embedding_policy=vector_embedding_policy,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    indexing_policy=indexing_policy,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_container_properties=cosmos_container_properties,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_database_properties=cosmos_database_properties,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    create_container=True,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    database_name=\\\"rag_chatbot_example\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    container_name=\\\"vector_store\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"storage_context = StorageContext.from_defaults(vector_store=store)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Index the data\\n\",\n",
    "    \"index = VectorStoreIndex.from_documents(documents, storage_context=storage_context)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"Vector index created successfully.\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a3b4c5d6-e7f8-9012-abcd-123456789012\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 6. Full Text Search Store Setup\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"For full text search and hybrid search types, a separate container with `full_text_policy` and `fullTextIndexes` is required. Create a `fts_store` that indexes the same documents with both vector and full text search enabled.\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"> **Note:** Full text search requires enabling the feature in your Cosmos DB for NoSQL account. See [Full Text Search in Azure Cosmos DB for NoSQL](https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/azure/cosmos-db/nosql/full-text-search).\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b4c5d6e7-f8a9-0123-bcde-234567890123\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Indexing policy with both vector and full text indexes\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fts_indexing_policy = {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"indexingMode\\\": \\\"consistent\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"includedPaths\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/*\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"excludedPaths\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": '/\\\"_etag\\\"/?'}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"vectorIndexes\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/embedding\\\", \\\"type\\\": \\\"quantizedFlat\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"fullTextIndexes\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/text\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Full text policy enabling full text search on the 'text' field\\n\",\n",
    "    \"full_text_policy = {\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"defaultLanguage\\\": \\\"en-US\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    \\\"fullTextPaths\\\": [{\\\"path\\\": \\\"/text\\\", \\\"language\\\": \\\"en-US\\\"}],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# Create full text search store\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fts_store = AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearch(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_client=client,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_embedding_policy=vector_embedding_policy,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    indexing_policy=fts_indexing_policy,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_policy=full_text_policy,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_container_properties=cosmos_container_properties,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    cosmos_database_properties=cosmos_database_properties,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    create_container=True,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    database_name=\\\"rag_chatbot_example\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    container_name=\\\"fts_store\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fts_storage_context = StorageContext.from_defaults(vector_store=fts_store)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"fts_index = VectorStoreIndex.from_documents(documents, storage_context=fts_storage_context)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(\\\"Full text search index created successfully.\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c5d6e7f8-a9b0-1234-cdef-345678901234\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 7. Search Types\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"The following sections demonstrate all 7 search types supported by `AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearch`. Each search type is accessed by passing `search_type` (an `AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType` enum value) to `store.query()`.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d6e7f8a9-b0c1-2345-defa-456789012345\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7a. Vector Search (default)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Standard nearest-neighbour search using `VectorDistance`, ordered by similarity score. This is the default behaviour and is equivalent to the original `_query` implementation.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e7f8a9b0-c1d2-3456-efab-567890123456\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Generate an embedding for the query\\n\",\n",
    "    \"query_text = \\\"object detection in autonomous driving\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"query_embedding = embed_model.get_text_embedding(query_text)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"vector_query = VectorStoreQuery(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    query_embedding=query_embedding,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    similarity_top_k=5,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector] Returned {len(results.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node, score in zip(results.nodes, results.similarities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  score={score:.4f}  id={node.node_id}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f8a9b0c1-d2e3-4567-fabc-678901234567\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7b. Vector Search with Score Threshold\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Same as vector search but filters results to only include nodes whose similarity score meets or exceeds a minimum `threshold`. Use this to avoid returning weakly-related results.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a9b0c1d2-e3f4-5678-abcd-789012345678\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_threshold = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR_SCORE_THRESHOLD,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    threshold=0.7,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector_score_threshold] Returned {len(results_threshold.nodes)} results (threshold=0.7)\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node, score in zip(results_threshold.nodes, results_threshold.similarities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  score={score:.4f}  id={node.node_id}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b0c1d2e3-f4a5-6789-bcde-890123456789\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7c. Full Text Search\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Uses a `FullTextContains` WHERE predicate to find documents that contain specific keywords. **No `query_embedding` is required.** Uses `fts_store` which has full text indexes configured.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c1d2e3f4-a5b6-7890-cdef-901234567890\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"fts_query = VectorStoreQuery(similarity_top_k=5)  # No query_embedding needed\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results_fts = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    fts_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.FULL_TEXT_SEARCH,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"object detection\\\"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[full_text_search] Returned {len(results_fts.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node in results_fts.nodes:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  id={node.node_id}  text_preview={node.get_content()[:80]}...\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d2e3f4a5-b6c7-8901-defa-012345678901\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7d. Full Text Ranking\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Uses `ORDER BY RANK FullTextScore(...)` for BM25-style ranking. Supports single or multi-field Reciprocal Rank Fusion (RRF). **No `query_embedding` is required.**\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e3f4a5b6-c7d8-9012-efab-123456789012\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Single-field full text ranking\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results_ftr = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    fts_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.FULL_TEXT_RANKING,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"neural network image recognition\\\"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[full_text_ranking] Returned {len(results_ftr.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node in results_ftr.nodes:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  id={node.node_id}  text_preview={node.get_content()[:80]}...\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f4a5b6c7-d8e9-0123-fabc-234567890123\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# Multi-field full text ranking (RRF across multiple search terms/fields)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results_ftr_multi = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    fts_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.FULL_TEXT_RANKING,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"convolutional neural network\\\"},\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"image segmentation\\\"},\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[full_text_ranking multi-field] Returned {len(results_ftr_multi.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node in results_ftr_multi.nodes:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  id={node.node_id}  text_preview={node.get_content()[:80]}...\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a5b6c7d8-e9f0-1234-abcd-345678901234\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7e. Hybrid Search\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Combines `FullTextScore` and `VectorDistance` using `ORDER BY RANK RRF(...)`. Both semantic similarity (via embeddings) and keyword relevance (via full text) contribute to the final ranking.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b6c7d8e9-f0a1-2345-bcde-456789012345\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"hybrid_query = VectorStoreQuery(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    query_embedding=query_embedding,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    similarity_top_k=5,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results_hybrid = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    hybrid_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.HYBRID,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"object detection in autonomous driving\\\"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[hybrid] Returned {len(results_hybrid.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node, score in zip(results_hybrid.nodes, results_hybrid.similarities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  score={score:.4f}  id={node.node_id}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c7d8e9f0-a1b2-3456-cdef-567890123456\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7f. Hybrid Search with Score Threshold\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Hybrid RRF search with an additional client-side score threshold filter. Results below the `threshold` are discarded after the server returns them.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d8e9f0a1-b2c3-4567-defa-678901234567\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_hybrid_threshold = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    hybrid_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.HYBRID_SCORE_THRESHOLD,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"object detection in autonomous driving\\\"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    threshold=0.6,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[hybrid_score_threshold] Returned {len(results_hybrid_threshold.nodes)} results (threshold=0.6)\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node, score in zip(results_hybrid_threshold.nodes, results_hybrid_threshold.similarities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  score={score:.4f}  id={node.node_id}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e9f0a1b2-c3d4-5678-efab-789012345678\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 7g. Weighted Hybrid Search\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Hybrid RRF search with client-side per-component weight re-ranking. The `weights` list assigns a float weight to each RRF component `[full_text, vector]`. This re-ranking is applied **after** the server returns results since CosmosDB SQL does not support weighted RRF natively.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f0a1b2c3-d4e5-6789-fabc-890123456789\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"# weights[0] = weight for full text component\\n\",\n",
    "    \"# weights[1] = weight for vector component\\n\",\n",
    "    \"results_weighted = fts_store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    hybrid_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.WEIGHTED_HYBRID_SEARCH,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    full_text_rank_filter=[\\n\",\n",
    "    \"        {\\\"search_field\\\": \\\"text\\\", \\\"search_text\\\": \\\"object detection in autonomous driving\\\"}\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    ],\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    weights=[0.3, 0.7],  # Favour semantic (vector) over keyword (full text)\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[weighted_hybrid_search] Returned {len(results_weighted.nodes)} results (weights=[0.3, 0.7])\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"for node, score in zip(results_weighted.nodes, results_weighted.similarities):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  score={score:.4f}  id={node.node_id}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567891\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 8. Advanced Query Options\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"All search types support additional query kwargs to control filtering, pagination, and projection.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678902\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 8a. WHERE Filter\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Pass a raw CosmosDB SQL WHERE predicate via the `where` kwarg to pre-filter documents before the vector search.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c3d4e5f6-a7b8-9012-cdef-123456789013\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_where = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    where=\\\"c.metadata.file_type = 'pdf'\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector + where filter] Returned {len(results_where.nodes)} results\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d4e5f6a7-b8c9-0123-defa-234567890124\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 8b. Offset / Limit (Pagination)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Use `offset_limit` for `OFFSET x LIMIT y` pagination. This replaces `TOP` for hybrid search types.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e5f6a7b8-c9d0-1234-efab-345678901235\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_paginated = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    offset_limit=\\\"OFFSET 0 LIMIT 3\\\",\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector + offset_limit] Returned {len(results_paginated.nodes)} results (page 1, size 3)\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f6a7b8c9-d0e1-2345-fabc-456789012346\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 8c. Projection Mapping\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Use `projection_mapping` to project specific Cosmos DB document fields into LlamaIndex node metadata keys.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a7b8c9d0-e1f2-3456-abcd-567890123457\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_proj = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    projection_mapping={\\\"metadata\\\": \\\"node_metadata\\\", \\\"text\\\": \\\"content\\\"},\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector + projection_mapping] Returned {len(results_proj.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"if results_proj.nodes:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(\\\"  Metadata keys:\\\", list(results_proj.nodes[0].metadata.keys()))\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"b8c9d0e1-f2a3-4567-bcde-678901234568\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"### 8d. Return with Vectors\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Set `return_with_vectors=True` to include the raw embedding vectors in the returned nodes.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"c9d0e1f2-a3b4-5678-cdef-789012345679\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"results_with_vectors = store.query(\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    vector_query,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    search_type=AzureCosmosDBNoSqlVectorSearchType.VECTOR,\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return_with_vectors=True,\\n\",\n",
    "    \")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"print(f\\\"[vector + return_with_vectors] Returned {len(results_with_vectors.nodes)} results\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"if results_with_vectors.nodes:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    embedding = results_with_vectors.nodes[0].embedding\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    print(f\\\"  Embedding dims: {len(embedding) if embedding else 'None'}\\\")\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"markdown\",\n",
    "   \"id\": \"d0e1f2a3-b4c5-6789-defa-890123456780\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"## 9. RAG Chatbot with Gradio UI\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"Build a simple RAG chatbot using the default vector query engine and a Gradio interface.\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"e1f2a3b4-c5d6-7890-efab-901234567881\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"import gradio as gr\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"query_engine = index.as_query_engine()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"def user_query(user_prompt, chat_history):\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    start_time = time.time()\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    response = query_engine.query(user_prompt)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    elapsed_ms = round((time.time() - start_time) * 1000, 2)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    details = f\\\"\\\\n\\\\n*(Time: {elapsed_ms}ms)*\\\"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chat_history.append([user_prompt, str(response) + details])\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    return gr.update(value=\\\"\\\"), chat_history\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"f2a3b4c5-d6e7-8901-fabc-012345678902\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"chat_history = []\\n\",\n",
    "    \"with gr.Blocks() as demo:\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    chatbot = gr.Chatbot(label=\\\"RAG Chatbot (vector search)\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    msg = gr.Textbox(label=\\\"Ask me anything about the CVPR 2019 papers!\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    clear = gr.Button(\\\"Clear\\\")\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    msg.submit(user_query, [msg, chatbot], [msg, chatbot], queue=False)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"    clear.click(lambda: None, None, chatbot, queue=False)\\n\",\n",
    "    \"\\n\",\n",
    "    \"demo.launch(debug=True)\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  },\n",
    "  {\n",
    "   \"cell_type\": \"code\",\n",
    "   \"execution_count\": null,\n",
    "   \"id\": \"a3b4c5d6-e7f8-9012-abcd-123456789013\",\n",
    "   \"metadata\": {},\n",
    "   \"outputs\": [],\n",
    "   \"source\": [\n",
    "    \"demo.close()\"\n",
    "   ]\n",
    "  }\n",
    " ],\n",
